            "reviews": "“Wee Free Studio’s Powargrid pumps out witty writing, devilish AI, and simply serious strategy.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://opnoobs.com/reviews/indie/strategy/powargrid\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >OPNoobs</a><br><br>“Winning a game of Powargrid isn't exactly an easy feat thanks to the intelligent AI that tries - and often succeeds - to outsmart the player at every turn.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://geeksnack.com/powargrid-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Geek Snack</a><br><br>“Powargrid is funny... and a very good game!”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.dumeegamer.com/reviews/dennis/powargrid.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >DumeeGamer</a><br>",
